<LI class=MsoNormal 0in .5in? list tab-stops: level1 l0 mso-list: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; lfo2;><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>Pet appear with the buffs already on it when it is summoned </SPAN>
<LI class=MsoNormal 0in .5in? list tab-stops: level1 l0 mso-list: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; lfo2;><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>Remove any root/snare/cancel magic spells from a pet’s lineup which primarily makes a pet un-useable for groups and raids</SPAN></LI></UL>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in .5in? list tab-stops: level1 l0 mso-list: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; lfo2;><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>4) Improved Damage shield</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Done</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>5) Streamline the item summoning process (more target summons)</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: 0.5in; 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>a) LORE tag on focus items. This is more of a hinderance than anything. Remove the LORE tag.<BR>b) Targeted summons. Makes giving out summoned items a </SPAN><namespace prefix = st1 ns = "http://www.lithium.com/unique/URI"><place><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>LOT</SPAN></place><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?> easier, and actually bypasses the LORE issue as well in most cases.<BR>c) Multiple item summons. This is more of a convenience factor. People want summons that summon a Muzzle, Girdle, and 2 pet weapons at once, all to the cursor, to make it a lot easier to give to the pet.</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: 0.5in; 0pt **Zowie**?MARGIN: auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?></SPAN><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being evaluated</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>6) Pet zones with you (Pet Issues/Requests)</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>This is in response to Pet Affinity, but we've also been asking for years. Given that you can buff your pet with Pet Affinity and get group buffs on the pet (especially group only buffs), but you can't keep the buffs on your pet when you zone (this is especially a problem for LDoN and GoD, where you don't buff at all inside the dungeon), this makes the ability less practical.</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>*suggestion - Add an AA that allows a suspended minion to zone</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently on test server, however there are no plans at this time to allow a suspended minion to zone.</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>7) Improve pet Heals (Pet Issues/Requests)</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>8) Improve off tanking in Gates Expansion (Pet Issues/Requests)</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>9) COH useable in more zones (make is useable in all corpse summoning zones)</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>Currently being discussed</FONT></SPAN><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?>10) Better utility in groups and raids</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: **Zowie**?MARGIN: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; auto?><SPAN **Zowie**?COLOR: Verdana? FONT-FAMILY: red;><FONT color=#ff0000>This one I need your help on, I know there are a ton of threads on these boards about this issue, let’s start one thread and get all of those ideas on how a magician’s raid and group utility can be improved.</FONT></SPAN><SPAN **Zowie**?FONT-FAMILY: Verdana?></SPAN></P></DIV></SPAN></DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
