<P class=MsoNormal 0pt 0in **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0.25in?><SPAN mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: Arial?><STRONG>Shield of Flame</STRONG></SPAN><SPAN mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: Arial?><BR>from 60 mana, 4 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 60 mana, 2.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Inferno Shield<BR></STRONG>from 80 mana, 3.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 80 mana, 2.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Barrier of Combustion<BR></STRONG>from 100 mana, 4.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 100 mana, 3 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Shield of Lava<BR></STRONG>from 120 mana, 4.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 120 mana, 3 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Boon of Immolation (group)<BR></STRONG>from 360 mana, 5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 300 mana, 3 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Cadeau of Flame</STRONG><BR>from 155 mana, 4.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 150 mana, 3 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Aegis of Ro (group)</STRONG><BR>from 450 mana, 9 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 350 mana, 3 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Flameshield of Ro<BR></STRONG>from 190 mana, 5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 180 mana, 2.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><STRONG>Maelstrom of Ro (group)</STRONG><BR>from 450 mana, 5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR>to 380 mana, 2.5 cast, 2.25 recast<BR><BR>These changes to the damage shields will insure, once and for all, that Magicians have the best and most efficient damage shields.</SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal 0in **SMURF**?MARGIN: 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none?><SPAN mso-bidi-font-family: Verdana; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY: Arial?>NOTE: Need Spell Casting Reinforcement AA to increase the duration, thus saving mana in the long run. </SPAN><SPAN Verdana? **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:></SPAN></P>
